Building Resident Engineer
- ,
Date Posted: 2014/05/04 11:40:37
Ref. JB3047090
Job Description
Building Structural Resident Engineer, Dubai based for an international engineering consultant Package 45-50,000 / month A global brand, our Clients are a multi-disciplined engineering consultant; with a global staff matrix and office network. They have been based in Dubai for over ten years, providing design engineering consultancy services to the United Arab Emirates, Qatar and Saudi Arabia clients. Reporting to the Program Manager and working with other specialist companies (architecture, quantity surveying, MEP), we are seeking for 5 star hotel and leisure development a Building Resident Engineer. You will represent our Client site based team for all site civil structural design queries, requests and to ensure the structural designs are done in accordance with the approved drawings.
Skills
To be considered you will need to have: Tertiary education from a recognizable university with professional qualifications; 12-15 years building structural design and site supervision consultancy experience; managing design onsite supervisory for 5+ start hotel developments in Dubai fOR Further information, please contact Ikram Rabbani on +971-55-585-2977.
